	(text "29: R_{IREF} = (V_{IREF} - V_{SS}) / I_{REF}\nV_{IREF} = 17V - 3V\nI_{REF} = 10uA\n=> R_{IREF} = (17V - 3V) / 10uA = 1M4 R\n=> 1M5 about 7% dimmer\n1M2 recommended by manufacturer\n1M still within bounds but 223uA vs 149uA consumption"
